OL,3,CPeston: Does Starmer win or lose from
OL,4,Cthe Trump rift?
OL,6,FKeir Starmer would not, I think,
OL,7,Faspire to be Winston Churchill (during
OL,8,Fthe general election, when I pressed
OL,9,Fhim to pick one hero from history, he
OL,10,Freluctantly alighted on Nelson
OL,11,FMandela).
OL,13,FAnd on the evidence of conversations
OL,14,Fwith his team, I didn't detect sadness
OL,15,Fthat Donald Trump has turned on him by
OL,16,Fdenigrating him as no reincarnation of
OL,17,FBritain's celebrated war-time leader.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
