OL,3,CPeston: Does Starmer win or lose from
OL,4,Cthe Trump rift?
OL,6,FParty politics explains that. The left
OL,7,Fof the Labour Party hated the way they
OL,8,Fsaw Starmer fawning to the American
OL,9,Fpresident for more than a year. And
OL,10,Fwhat looked to them like appeasement
OL,11,Fhelped the Green Party under Polanski
OL,12,Fwin votes in the Gorton and Denton by-
OL,13,Felection and support more broadly.
OL,15,FSo maybe Starmer's refusal, initially,
OL,16,Fto allow Trump to use British bases
OL,17,Fincluding Diego Garcia for its war
OL,18,Fagainst Iran - which is what sparked
OL,19,FTrump's fury - will temper the Green
OL,20,Fsurge.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
