OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772629888
OL,3,CPeston: Does Starmer win or lose from
OL,4,Cthe Trump rift?
OL,6,FBut economics and politics are at odds
OL,7,Fhere. And the economics may yet
OL,8,Frebound on Starmer.
OL,10,FBecause a vindictive Trump may punish
OL,11,FStarmer by shredding the preferential
OL,12,Ftariffs, for car manufacturers and
OL,13,Fother exporters, that the prime
OL,14,Fminister secured as a result of wooing
OL,15,FTrump.
OL,17,FAnd that would be both costly for the
OL,18,FUK and humiliating for Starmer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
