OL,3,CPeston: Does Starmer win or lose from
OL,4,Cthe Trump rift?
OL,6,FThat said, the evidence of opinion
OL,7,Fpolls is that a majority of British
OL,8,Fpeople do not want the UK to go to war
OL,9,Fagainst Iran, and they are not Trump
OL,10,Ffans.
OL,12,FSo again the rift may not be
OL,13,Fpolitically costly to the PM.
OL,15,FBut there is another but. Namely, that
OL,16,Fwe are now allowing the US to use our
OL,17,Fair bases. And most people won't
OL,18,Funderstand the PM's logic in saying no
OL,19,Fto US fighter jets a few days ago and
OL,20,Fyes today.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
