OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772629888
OL,3,CPeston: Does Starmer win or lose from
OL,4,Cthe Trump rift?
OL,6,FThe logic, for Starmer, is that his
OL,7,Fattorney general Richard Hermer told
OL,8,Fhim it was unlawful for America to use
OL,9,Four bases when America was the
OL,10,Faggressor and before Tehran had
OL,11,Fretaliated but it became lawful when
OL,12,FTehran started dropping bombs on our
OL,13,FGulf and Arab allies.
OL,15,FVoters may well accept that is
OL,16,Finternational law. And they may also
OL,17,Fsay that if so the law is an ass.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
